    <note>Lu(5) Gui [7049] Zhen's [3634] son, Dian's [8098], Bi's [7051] and Zhuan's [7297] father, Zhi's [1284] and Zai's [1288] grandfather, Qi's [7048] brother. His wife was Bian(1) Xun's [7061] sister and Bian(1) Su's [7317] granddaughter. Gui was Wu(3) Xiaoneng's [1972] grandfather-in-law. His sister was the wife of Yang(2) Daya's [2029] son, Hang [4042]. His maternal grandfather, Wu(3) Zhi [4007], was from Jianyang, but had the same generational name as one lineage of the Jianning, Pucheng Wu(3). Lu Dian, WJ, 15.13a-14b, 16.16a-18b (wife, born Bian, who died in 1093 at age 69); Su Song, WJ, 59.14b-17b. CBD, 3, 2652.</note>
